<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">University of the Arts</h2>
<strong>Philadelphia, PA</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-red">No</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>The University of the Arts may award 3 credits toward the liberal arts requirements for a score of 4 or better in any College Board AP Examination in an academic subject. AP credit is not given for studio art or performance.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://catalog.uarts.edu/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

